The "u2up.build" project serves as a template for building software projects.

Features:
=========

Native Build using make directly:
================
Configure only:
--------------
~/PROJECT$\
 env BUILDIR=../build PREFIX=/usr/local ./configure 

Compile only:
------------
~/PROJECT$\
 make

Installation:
------------
~/PROJECT$\
 env DESTDIR=$(pwd)/../install make install

Clean:
------
~/PROJECT$\
 make clean

---
End!

